author: By Eric Scigliano
title: Letter From Your City’s Future
description: A week ahead on the outbreak curve, Seattle’s already resorting to motel hospitals and bandana masks. And we’re the best case scenario.
content: It wont be pretty, even after you get used to empty store shelves and restaurants, gyms and other public establishments being closed. Be prepared for field hospitals, triage plans and campaigns to fabricate hospital protective gear from hardware store materia… [+14024 chars]
